---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - Rufus Plaga">
  <div class="w-full mx-auto pt-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-12 text-left scroll-fade">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16 scroll-fade">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
          Hi, I'm <span class="font-semibold text-red-600">Rufus Plaga</span>, a Media Design student 
          with a passion for 3D visualization, UI/UX design, and brand identity.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          I'm currently studying Media Design (B.Sc.) and specialize in the creative intersection 
          between design and technology. My goal is to develop visual concepts that are not only 
          aesthetically pleasing but also functionally compelling.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600">Quick Facts</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-600 mr-2">▸</span>
            <span>Media Design Student (B.Sc.)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-600 mr-2">▸</span>
            <span>Specialization: 3D & Brand Design</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-600 mr-2">▸</span>
            <span>Location: Weingarten, Germany</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 scroll-fade">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">Skills & Expertise</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-red-600">3D Modeling & Rendering</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            Creating photorealistic 3D visualizations and product renderings with 
            professional tools.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Blender</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SolidWorks</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">KeyShot</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-red-600">UI/UX Design</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            Designing intuitive user interfaces with a focus on user experience 
            and modern design trends.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Figma</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Adobe XD</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Prototyping</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-red-600">Graphic Design</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            Developing visual concepts for print and digital media with the complete 
            Adobe Creative Cloud workflow.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Photoshop</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Illustrator</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">InDesign</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-red-600">Brand Design</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
            Conceptualizing and implementing cohesive brand identities from logo 
            to corporate design.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Logo Design</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Style Guides</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Branding</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 scroll-fade">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">My Approach</h2>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-slate-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-red-100">
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          My approach combines creative thinking with technical precision. I place great emphasis 
          on clear communication and an iterative design process that focuses on feedback and 
          continuous improvement.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-700">
          From initial concept to final implementation, I work in a structured and 
          goal-oriented manner to realize projects that are both visually impressive and 
          optimally fulfill their function.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-fade">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">Interested in Working Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6">
        I'm always excited about new projects and creative challenges. 
        Feel free to reach out for a no-obligation inquiry.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:plagarufus@gmail.com" 
         class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors font-heading font-medium">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
